data.description: Located in the heart of Baldwin county in Robertsdale, Alabama you're just a little over 20 miles away from the beautiful beaches of Gulf Shores and Orange Beach and even closer to Foley and the eastern shore!  You'll love the open floor plan and new wood floor. But maybe the best thing about this property is that it has a huge yard that is a full acre with big beautiful trees!  Very quiet and laid back area.  Nice barn/shed and single car port. Lots of potential!
